location.fullValue: The Sequoia A with 3-Car Garage Plan, Sunterra

data.description: This beautiful home is PERFECT for family gatherings has a great nice size back yard with a gorgeous wooden above-ground pool deck along with customized flooring tile pattern. Great to just chill back in the summer. House is full of delights including spacious kitchen with a white tile backsplash. Living area is separated in two spaces that can be used as you like. Upstairs are all three bedrooms and game room which is ideal to turn into an extra room because of the RUSTIC sliding barn doors that are added for privacy. Neighborhood is very FRIENDLY  includes amenities such as multiple playgrounds for kids, Splash pad, lakes, jogging trails and many more. This will not last long!
